org.datavec.api.transform.sequence

Class ReduceSequenceTransform

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.datavec.api.transform.sequence.ReduceSequenceTransform
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, ColumnOp, Transform

    public class ReduceSequenceTransform
extends java.lang.Object
implements Transform
    Reduce The values in each column in the sequence to a single value using a reducer. Note: after applying ReduceSequenceTransform, you have sequences of length 1. Consequently, this transform is often used in conjunction with ConvertFromSequence
    See Also:
